#: includes/class-cookie-manager.php:219
msgid "Required for site functionality (e.g. login, preferences)."
msgstr "Erforderlich für die Funktionalität der Website (z. B. Anmeldung, Einstellungen)."

#: includes/class-cookie-manager.php:249
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Name"

#: includes/class-cookie-manager.php:250
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beschreibung"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:152
msgid "Currently, all cookies we use are essential for the website to operate. We do not use cookies to track you outside of this website. We care about your privacy. ❤️"
msgstr "Derzeit sind alle von uns verwendeten Cookies für den Betrieb der Website erforderlich. Wir verwenden keine Cookies, um Sie außerhalb dieser Website zu verfolgen. Ihre Privatsphäre ist uns wichtig. ❤️"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:180
msgid "We use cookies to ensure the site works and to improve your experience. You can accept all, only essential, or manage preferences."
msgstr "Wir verwenden Cookies, damit die Website funktioniert und um Ihre Erfahrung zu verbessern. Sie können alle akzeptieren, nur notwendige oder Einstellungen verwalten."

#: includes/class-frontend.php:186
msgid "Privacy policy"
msgstr "Datenschutzerklärung"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:190
msgid "We use cookies"
msgstr "Wir verwenden Cookies"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:192
msgid "Accept all"
msgstr "Alle akzeptieren"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:193
msgid "Essential only"
msgstr "Nur notwendige"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:194
msgid "Manage preferences"
msgstr "Einstellungen verwalten"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:195
msgid "Cookie preferences"
msgstr "Cookie-Einstellungen"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:196
msgid "Save preferences"
msgstr "Einstellungen speichern"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:197
msgid "Close"
msgstr "Schließen"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:198
msgid "Essential cookies"
msgstr "Notwendige Cookies"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:199
msgid "These cookies are required for the website to function (e.g. login, security, preferences)."
msgstr "Diese Cookies sind für die Funktionalität der Website erforderlich (z. B. Anmeldung, Sicherheit, Einstellungen)."

#: includes/class-frontend.php:200
msgid "Non-essential cookies"
msgstr "Nicht notwendige Cookies"

#: includes/class-frontend.php:201
msgid "These cookies are used for analytics or third-party features. You can disable them."
msgstr "Diese Cookies werden für Analysen oder Drittanbieter-Funktionen verwendet. Sie können sie deaktivieren."

#: includes/class-frontend.php:202
msgid "We have updated our cookie policy. Please review and accept again."
msgstr "Wir haben unsere Cookie-Richtlinie aktualisiert. Bitte prüfen und erneut akzeptieren."

#: includes/class-rest-controller.php:140
msgid "Login required."
msgstr "Anmeldung erforderlich."

#: includes/class-rest-controller.php:186
msgid "Security check failed."
msgstr "Sicherheitsüberprüfung fehlgeschlagen."

#: includes/class-rest-controller.php:152
msgid "Not allowed."
msgstr "Nicht erlaubt."

#: includes/class-rest-controller.php:190
msgid "Not logged in."
msgstr "Nicht angemeldet."

#: includes/class-rest-controller.php:197
msgid "Invalid consent data."
msgstr "Ungültige Einwilligungsdaten."

#: includes/class-settings.php:90
msgid "Oven Cookie Consent"
msgstr "Oven Cookie-Einwilligung"

#: includes/class-settings.php:91
msgid "Oven"
msgstr "Oven"

#: includes/class-settings.php:113
msgid "Cookie Consent"
msgstr "Cookie-Einwilligung"

#: includes/class-settings.php:121
msgid "Enable cookie consent"
msgstr "Cookie-Einwilligung aktivieren"

#: includes/class-settings.php:128
msgid "Show the cookie consent modal to visitors."
msgstr "Das Cookie-Einwilligungs-Modal Besuchern anzeigen."

#: includes/class-settings.php:134
msgid "Cookie detection mode"
msgstr "Cookie-Erkennungsmodus"

#: includes/class-settings.php:141
msgid "When enabled (and you are logged in as an administrator), browsing the site will detect cookies and add them to the list. New cookies trigger a revision so all visitors must re-accept."
msgstr "Wenn aktiviert (und Sie als Administrator angemeldet sind), werden beim Surfen auf der Website Cookies erkannt und zur Liste hinzugefügt. Neue Cookies lösen eine Überarbeitung aus, sodass alle Besucher erneut zustimmen müssen."

#: includes/class-settings.php:156
msgid "Hide from guests"
msgstr "Vor Gästen ausblenden"

#: includes/class-settings.php:163
msgid "When checked, the cookie consent modal is only shown to logged-in users. Guests will not see the banner."
msgstr "Wenn aktiviert, wird das Cookie-Einwilligungsfenster nur angemeldeten Nutzern angezeigt. Gäste sehen das Banner nicht."

#: includes/class-settings.php:147
msgid "Privacy policy URL"
msgstr "URL der Datenschutzerklärung"

#: includes/class-settings.php:156
#: includes/class-settings.php:599
msgid "Optional. If set, a link to your privacy policy is shown in the consent modal (recommended for GDPR)."
msgstr "Optional. Wenn gesetzt, wird im Einwilligungs-Modal ein Link zu Ihrer Datenschutzerklärung angezeigt (empfohlen für die DSGVO)."

#: includes/class-settings.php:425
msgid "Configure how Oven displays the cookie consent banner and detects cookies."
msgstr "Konfigurieren Sie, wie Oven das Cookie-Einwilligungs-Banner anzeigt und Cookies erkennt."

#: includes/class-settings.php:443
msgid "Add cookie manually"
msgstr "Cookie manuell hinzufügen"

#: includes/class-settings.php:444
msgid "Cookie name"
msgstr "Cookie-Name"

#: includes/class-settings.php:527
#: includes/class-settings.php:544
msgid "Essential"
msgstr "Notwendig"

#: includes/class-settings.php:528
#: includes/class-settings.php:544
#: includes/class-user-consent-profile.php:158
msgid "Non-essential"
msgstr "Nicht notwendig"

#: includes/class-settings.php:449
msgid "Optional: script URL to block until consent (non-essential only)"
msgstr "Optional: Script-URL zum Blockieren bis zur Einwilligung (nur nicht notwendige)"

#: includes/class-settings.php:451
msgid "Optional: description (what this cookie does, shown to visitors)"
msgstr "Optional: Beschreibung (was dieses Cookie macht, wird Besuchern angezeigt)"

#: includes/class-settings.php:452
msgid "e.g. Remembers your language preference"
msgstr "z. B. Merkt sich Ihre Spracheinstellung"

#: includes/class-settings.php:453
msgid "Add cookie"
msgstr "Cookie hinzufügen"

#: includes/class-settings.php:456
msgid "Cookies detected on your site. You can override classification and set a description for each cookie so visitors see what it does in the consent modal."
msgstr "Auf Ihrer Website erkannte Cookies. Sie können die Klassifizierung überschreiben und für jedes Cookie eine Beschreibung festlegen, die Besucher im Einwilligungs-Modal sehen."

#: includes/class-settings.php:460
msgid "Detected cookies list"
msgstr "Liste der erkannten Cookies"

#: includes/class-settings.php:461
msgid "Description (shown to visitors)"
msgstr "Beschreibung (wird Besuchern angezeigt)"

#: includes/class-settings.php:461
msgid "Actions"
msgstr "Aktionen"

#: includes/class-settings.php:463
msgid "No cookies detected yet. Enable cookie detection mode and browse your site."
msgstr "Noch keine Cookies erkannt. Aktivieren Sie den Cookie-Erkennungsmodus und surfen Sie auf Ihrer Website."

#: includes/class-settings.php:480
msgid "Revert to auto"
msgstr "Auf automatisch zurücksetzen"

#: includes/class-settings.php:500
msgid "Mark as essential"
msgstr "Als notwendig markieren"

#: includes/class-settings.php:502
msgid "Mark as non-essential"
msgstr "Als nicht notwendig markieren"

#: includes/class-settings.php:506
msgid "overridden"
msgstr "überschrieben"

#: includes/class-settings.php:508
msgid "What this cookie does (optional)"
msgstr "Was dieses Cookie macht (optional)"

#: includes/class-settings.php:508
msgid "Description for"
msgstr "Beschreibung für"

#: includes/class-settings.php:513
msgid "Save descriptions"
msgstr "Beschreibungen speichern"

#: includes/class-settings.php:520
msgid "Classification by pattern"
msgstr "Klassifizierung nach Muster"

#: includes/class-settings.php:521
msgid "Cookies whose name contains the text below will be classified as essential or non-essential. For example, any cookie with \"stripe\" in the name can be marked essential."
msgstr "Cookies, deren Name den folgenden Text enthält, werden als notwendig oder nicht notwendig eingestuft. Z. B. kann jedes Cookie mit \"stripe\" im Namen als notwendig markiert werden."

#: includes/class-settings.php:524
msgid "Pattern (substring in cookie name)"
msgstr "Muster (Teilzeichenkette im Cookie-Namen)"

#: includes/class-settings.php:525
msgid "e.g. stripe"
msgstr "z. B. stripe"

#: includes/class-settings.php:526
msgid "Classification"
msgstr "Klassifizierung"

#: includes/class-settings.php:531
msgid "Add pattern rule"
msgstr "Musterregel hinzufügen"

#: includes/class-settings.php:534
msgid "Pattern overrides"
msgstr "Muster-Überschreibungen"

#: includes/class-settings.php:534
msgid "Pattern (contains)"
msgstr "Muster (enthält)"

#: includes/class-settings.php:534
msgid "Action"
msgstr "Aktion"

#: includes/class-settings.php:544
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "Entfernen"

#: includes/class-settings.php:548
msgid "No pattern rules yet."
msgstr "Noch keine Musterregeln."

#: includes/class-settings.php:554
msgid "Scripts that set non-essential cookies are blocked until the user opts in. If you mark a cookie as essential above, its script is no longer blocked."
msgstr "Scripts, die nicht notwendige Cookies setzen, werden blockiert, bis der Benutzer zustimmt. Wenn Sie ein Cookie oben als notwendig markieren, wird sein Script nicht mehr blockiert."

#: includes/class-settings.php:555
msgid "Blocked scripts list"
msgstr "Liste der blockierten Scripts"

#: includes/class-settings.php:556
msgid "Script URL"
msgstr "Script-URL"

#: includes/class-settings.php:556
msgid "Sets cookies"
msgstr "Setzt Cookies"

#: includes/class-settings.php:608
msgid "You do not have sufficient permissions to access this page."
msgstr "Sie haben keine ausreichenden Berechtigungen, um auf diese Seite zuzugreifen."

#: includes/class-settings.php:617
msgid "Save settings"
msgstr "Einstellungen speichern"

#: includes/class-settings.php:632
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Einstellungen"

#: includes/class-settings.php:156
msgid "Detected cookies"
msgstr "Erkannte Cookies"

#: includes/class-user-consent-profile.php:70
msgid "Cookie consent"
msgstr "Cookie-Einwilligung"

#: includes/class-user-consent-profile.php:66
msgid "No consent recorded for this user. Consent is only stored when the user is logged in and accepts or changes cookie preferences on the site."
msgstr "Keine Einwilligung für diesen Benutzer erfasst. Die Einwilligung wird nur gespeichert, wenn der Benutzer angemeldet ist und Cookie-Einstellungen auf der Website akzeptiert oder ändert."

#: includes/class-user-consent-profile.php:73
msgid "Current consent"
msgstr "Aktuelle Einwilligung"

#: includes/class-user-consent-profile.php:78
